## Location field

This field type is used to collect real world address and coordinates. It requires a [Map Provider](docs.getvoxel.io_articles_map-providers-and-settings_.md) to be enabled and configured in [Voxel Settings.](docs.getvoxel.io_articles_map-providers-and-settings_.md)

## General options

- Field name
- Field key
- Description
- Is Required
- CSS Classes
- Default value
